Class Recipe

java.lang.Object
com.example.demo.model.Recipe
public class Recipe extends Object
Model class representing a Recipe. Contains information about a recipe and provides methods to access and modify this information.

  • Constructor Details

    • Recipe

      public Recipe(String recipeId, String recipeName, String ingredients, String instructions, String mealType, byte[] recipeImage)
      Parameterized constructor for the Recipe class. Initializes a new Recipe object with the specified details.
      Parameters:
      recipeId - the unique ID of the recipe, if null a new UUID will be generated
      recipeName - the name of the recipe
      ingredients - the ingredients of the recipe
      instructions - the instructions for the recipe
      mealType - the type of meal (e.g., breakfast, lunch, dinner)
      recipeImage - the image of the recipe as a byte array
